===Sports===
The programme of the 2012 Summer Paralympics featured events in 20 sports.<ref name=guardian-massmarket>{{cite news|title=Paralympics organisers feel London is launchpad for mass-market Games|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/sport/2012/aug/25/paralympics-london-fever-impetus?newsfeed=true |accessdate=3 October 2013 | work = [[The Guardian]]|first=Owen |last=Gibson |date=25 August 2012}}</ref> The number of events in each sport is noted in parentheses.

{{Col-begin|width=100%}}
{{col-begin}}{{col-break}}
{{Col-1-of-3}}
*[[File:Archery pictogram (Paralympics).svg|17px]] [[Paralympic archery|Archery]]  <small>(9)</small> ({{detailslink|Archery at the 2012 Summer Paralympics}})
