The official schedule was published on 25 August 2011.<ref name="BBC Schedule">{{cite news| url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/disability_sport/14662054.stm | publisher=BBC News | title=2012 Paralympic schedule revealed | date=25 August 2011}}</ref>

